title: Maui By Keep It 100 (Maui Blast)
description: Maui Blast formerly known as Tropical Blast is a delectable blend of exotic guava juice and tropical fruits. The inhale has a sweet guava taste that will cause your mouth to drool like a waterfall. Upon exhaling is when the apple, watermelon, lychee, raspberry all come into play and complements the sweet fruity inhale perfectly.
